<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta http-equiv="content-type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8">
    <title>aula-js-005-darkmode.html</title>
    <meta name="author" content="Eduardo Ono">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/jquery@3.5.1/dist/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fancyapps/fancybox@3.5.7/dist/jquery.fancybox.min.css">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fancyapps/fancybox@3.5.7/dist/jquery.fancybox.min.js"></script>
    <style type="text/css">
      /* body */
      body {
        margin: 10%;
      }
    	.light-mode {
        color: black;
        background: white;
      }
      .dark-mode {
        color: white;
        background: black;
      }
      /* a */
      .dark-mode a:link {
        color: #66ffff;
        text-decoration: none;
      }
      .dark-mode a:visited {
        color: #ff99ff;
        text-decoration: none;
      }
      .dark-mode a:hover {
        text-decoration: underline overline;
      }
      .dark-mode a:active {
        color: #ff0000;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body class="light-mode">
    <h1>Desenvolvimento Web (JavaScript)</h1>
    <p><br>
    </p>
    <p>Executando código JavaScript:</p>
    <p>Link (Opçao 1): <a href="javascript:lightMode()">light-mode</a></p>
    <p>Link (Opção 2): <a href="javascript:;" onclick="javascript:darkMode()">dark-mode</a></p>
    <p> <a href="javascript:darkMode()"><img src="night-mode.png" alt="" style="width: 108px; height: 60px;"><br>
      </a></p>
    <p><br>
    </p>
    <div style="text-align: center;"><a data-fancybox href="night-mode.png"><img src="night-mode.png"

          alt="" style="width: 286px; height: 160px;"></a></div>
    <p> </p>
    <div id="caju"> </div>
    <script type="text/javascript">
      // var vetor = document.getElementsByTag("p");
      // alert(vetor[1].innerHTML);
    	function lightMode() {
        document.body.className = "light-mode";
        document.getElementById("caju").innerHTML = '<img src="night-mode.png" alt="" style="width: 108px; height: 60px;">';
      }
      function darkMode() {
        document.body.className = "dark-mode";
      }
    </script>
    <p></p>
  </body>
</html>
